<br>
A newbie paladin or cleric will always outpull a newbie monk.  Pacify is cheap.  But a skilled paladin/cleric will never approach the abilities of a skilled monk.  If you doubt me, then you have never had the honor of being grouped with a skilled monk.<br>
<br>
